          "text": "## m2-tls-h2-runtime complete\n\n**PR:** https://github.com/li-langverse/lic/pull/175 (branch `cursor/httpd-plan-continue`, commit `4ddc52a`)\n\n### What shipped\nLive `build/li-httpd` now terminates **TLS 1.3** (OpenSSL 3 via `dlopen`, no libssl-dev link) and negotiates **ALPN** (`h2`, `http/1.1`) on the Li epoll accept path. A minimal **HTTP/2** handler serves `GET /health` with `200` + body `ok\\n`.\n\n| Area | Files |\n|------|--------|\n| TLS runtime | `runtime/li_rt_tls.c`, `runtime/li_rt_tls.h` |\n| HTTP/2 runtime | `runtime/li_rt_h2.c`, `runtime/li_rt_h2.h` |\n| Integration | `runtime/li_rt_net.c`, `packages/li-net-httpd/src/lib.li`, `std/runtime/seam.li` |\n| Build/link | `compiler/codegen/compile.cpp`, `scripts/build-li-httpd.sh`, `runtime/CMakeLists.txt` |\n| Smoke | `packages/li-net-httpd/examples/tls_h2.toml`, `scripts/test-m2-tls-h2-runtime.sh`, `scripts/httpd-plan-gates.sh` |\n| Plan/docs | `docs/superpowers/plans/2026-05-16-li-httpd-plan.md` (`m2-tls-h2-runtime` → **completed**), `docs/release-notes/2026-05-23-httpd-m2-tls-h2-runtime.md` |\n\n### Tests run\n```bash\n./scripts/build-li-httpd.sh\n./scripts/test-m2-tls-h2-runtime.sh\nHTTPD_BENCH_SKIP_TIMING=1 ./scripts/httpd-plan-gates.sh\n```\n\n### Notes\n- TLS-only configs route through `httpd_upstream_proxy_epoll_loop` (no upstream required).\n- Server ALPN uses `SSL_CTX_set_alpn_select_cb` so curl negotiates `h2`.\n- HTTP/2 is intentionally minimal (health smoke); full HPACK/streaming is follow-up.\n- **Live benchmarks/Pages:** not refreshed (`SKIP_BENCH=1` — no new bench CSV for this runtime slice).\n\n## Agent deliverable\n- [x] Branch pushed and PR updated (#175)\n- [x] CI triggered on PR\n- [x] Tests added / updated — `scripts/test-m2-tls-h2-runtime.sh`, `scripts/httpd-plan-gates.sh`\n- [x] `./scripts/httpd-plan-gates.sh` green (with `HTTPD_BENCH_SKIP_TIMING=1`)\n- [ ] merge-approved (human)"
